a_for_lane` helper matches the pattern of other metadata-enrichment functions in `music_tracker.py`.\n- The test suite structure is consistent with other pipeline tests.\n\n## Security\n**PASS.** No security issues, secrets, or unsafe practices identified. The changes are limited to music metadata propagation and analysis.\n\n## Quality\n**PASS.** \n- 27 new tests in `tests/test_counterpoint_pipeline.py` pass.\n- All 2615 tests in the project pass, ensuring no regressions.\n- The code is clean, well-documented, and properly typed.\n\n## Issues Found\n- None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe wiring is complete and the validation logic is sound. Although `validate_scene_counterpoint` is currently only called in the tests, it is ready for integration into the main `validate_scene` or a self-critique loop as needed. The metadata propagation from score to tracker lanes is fully operational.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-018 @20260416t054258zd-verify.md"}}
